Here's a PlantUML component diagram focusing on the deployment aspect of the CompassUTD system:

```plantuml
@startuml DanNguyenN_CompassUTD

!define GCP #4285F4
!define MONGODB #47A248

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<GCP>> GCP
  BorderColor<<GCP>> #3367D6
  BackgroundColor<<MONGODB>> MONGODB
  BorderColor<<MONGODB>> #3F9142
}

cloud "Google Cloud Platform" {
  [Google Cloud Run] <<GCP>> as GCR
  [Vertex AI] <<GCP>> as VAI
  [PaLM 2 LLM] <<GCP>> as PaLM2
}

database "MongoDB Atlas" <<MONGODB>> as MongoDB

[FastAPI Application] as FastAPI
[CompassUTD Inference] as Inference
[Langchain Agent] as LangchainAgent
[CompassToolkit] as Toolkit

package "Information Retrieval Tools" {
  [Course Search]
  [Degree Search]
  [General UTD Info Search]
  [Definition Lookup]
  [RateMyProfessor Data]
}

[Web Scraping Layer] as WebScraper

GCR -- FastAPI
FastAPI -- Inference
Inference -- LangchainAgent
LangchainAgent -- Toolkit
Toolkit -- [Information Retrieval Tools]
[Information Retrieval Tools] -- WebScraper
FastAPI -- MongoDB : Stores chat history
Inference -- VAI : Uses
VAI -- PaLM2 : Leverages

@enduml
```